Technical Support Engineer
03 May 2014 02:39 AM - UAE
Technical Support EngineerApply now Job no: 769827Location: Dubai Dubai Head Office IT The Alshaya eGroup is a diverse organisation supporting corporate, warehouse and retail specific IT infrastructure and systems. We have software teams creating and developing in-house applications and product teams optimising and integrating major third party solutions. The rate of growth across divisions and geographies means we are constantly evaluating how we provide robust, scalable and business enabling infrastructure and systems in line with global benchmark standards. The Role:The Technical Support Engineer is responsible for providing first line support to retail stores by configuring and installing Windows servers, upgrading and migrating operating systems and software applications and handling user complaints and problems by providing ultimate solutions to meet their needs and requirements.  Additionally you will manage backups, troubleshoots and maintain secure data communication.Qualifications & Requirements:A university degree in electronics or computer engineeringHave previous experience in a similar roleVery good working knowledge of Windows Desktop and Server OSBasic networking skills (Windows or Networking certification is an added advantage)IT hardware troubleshooting skillsSecure data communication skillsBasic working knowledge in SQL/Sybase is an advantageKnowledge of Windows administrationExperien (more...)
